{"tid":163000,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"\"因為應用程式的並列設定不正確\"開唔到SPSS","createTime":"2017-03-19T16:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-21T17:12:54.000Z","uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa0f333fef37275be3a5d9ced8a4d892afe94f12","tid":163000,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:02:06.000Z","msg":"裝完SPSS想開就出現依句野<br />\n「因為應用程式的並列設定不正確，所以無法啟動。如需詳細資訊，請參閱應用程式事件記錄檔，或使用命令列工具 sxstrace.exe 。」<br />\n<br />\n之後上網搵到話要裝返visual studio c++<br />\n但想問下裝visual studio c++依步<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.visualstudio.com/zh-hant/thank-you-downloading-visual-studio/?sku=Community&amp;rel=15\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.visualstudio.com%2Fzh-hant%2Fthank-you-downloading-visual-studio%2F%3Fsku%3DCommunity%26rel%3D15&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=800a3855\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.visualstudio.com/zh-hant/thank-you-downloading-visual-studio/?sku=Community&amp;rel=15</a><br />\n裝完都有上面句野<br />\n到底可以點解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6855bc8390de374ad549190289fff347e8b265","tid":163000,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:05:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=300&amp;t=3866325\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobile01.com%2Ftopicdetail.php%3Ff%3D300%26t%3D3866325&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=842292b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mobile01.com/topicdetail.php?f=300&amp;t=3866325</a><br />\n依個方面都試左<br />\n但第2步打完trace都出現error<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cb8cb4f85ebf82746322132a498542e7c143a9","tid":163000,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T16:19:37.000Z","msg":"<img src